title: Skyworth: Jiuzhaigou Valley UHD 4K Demo
overview: Filmed in Ultra-HD by Skyworth in Jiuzhaigou Valley, a nature reserve and national park located in the north of Sichuan province, China. It is praised as a realm of magical fairytale, which is why its bountiful wildlife, colorful lakes, gushing waterfalls, luxuriant forests and mountains has drawn tourists for years.
